- Mix all the dry ingredients.
- Add the water gradually.
- Knead for 15 minutes.
- Fermentation for an hour avoiding drafts.
- Degas carefully and shape.
- Let rise for 45 minutes and preheat the oven to 250C.
- Bake with steam for the first 15 minutes at 250C.
- Lower the temperature to 200C and continue baking for 30 minutes more.